00:03:26.920 --> 00:03:32.440
solid, every morning, I would
wake up at about 4:00 AM,

00:03:32.440 --> 00:03:37.010
and I would pray
to God for Marcy.

00:03:37.010 --> 00:03:39.610
And Marcy came.

00:03:39.610 --> 00:03:41.110
I wasn't praying
for her by name.

00:03:41.110 --> 00:03:46.870
[LAUGHS] But I knew in the
deepest fiber of my being

00:03:46.870 --> 00:03:50.050
that Marcy was out
there, and I just wanted

00:03:50.050 --> 00:03:52.490
God to finally bring her to me.

00:03:55.100 --> 00:03:59.210
I knew it as truly as I
knew it that I was a woman.

00:03:59.210 --> 00:04:02.240
I knew that despite what
my body was telling me,

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:05.140
what everybody else in
my life was telling me,

00:04:05.140 --> 00:04:06.470
that I was a woman.

00:04:06.470 --> 00:04:09.710
I also knew that
Marcy was out there.

00:04:09.710 --> 00:04:14.540
So when Marcy says
just because, the story

00:04:14.540 --> 00:04:17.180
goes a little bit
deeper than that.

00:04:17.180 --> 00:04:19.190
I'm so proud of her that
